{"tid":2343003,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"三上悠亞出首本花魁寫真集 貼露體照試水溫","createTime":"2020-12-27T14:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T16:21:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8d6cee4a8e034c0e1d13f3c36027dc958fe6ee73","tid":2343003,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:34:07.000Z","msg":"原名鬼頭桃菜的三上悠亞，由偶像組合SKE48成員搖身一變成為AV界天后，在亞洲各地均有市場，先後來港拍戲、開見面會，又組女團進軍K-pop界，今年還為大馬創作鬼才黃明志的歌曲《不小心》拍MV，稱得上是當今AV界最吃得開的佼佼者。<br />\n<br />\n三上悠亞貴為暗黑界最具代表性人物，她同時活躍社交網，連日來也勤力更新Twitter和IG，自拍靚相與粉絲倒數2021年來臨。三上悠亞的工作已排至明年中，她宣佈2月將推出全新寫真集《和美寫美》，首次以花魁作為主題，屆時亦會舉行見面會答謝支持者。近日，成人雜誌《週刊實話》就公開三上悠亞的全新花魁寫真，讓Fans們先睹為快，三上悠亞亦在Twitter貼出今次的造型照為粉絲止渴，可見她真空上陣露出下陰，引起網民瘋狂轉發及讚好。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xpOGp1YhEqOzHR7KWmfeJpP1Drk=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RKFZJGU6CBAYLERZYRGMKKCDVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxpOGp1YhEqOzHR7KWmfeJpP1Drk%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRKFZJGU6CBAYLERZYRGMKKCDVQ.jpg&h=fd0e6e95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7e40tK9XqeJRb4qx2hDVrF4Ja7A=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G2O5ICXWRJCDFEMJKFI2P5OYSI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7e40tK9XqeJRb4qx2hDVrF4Ja7A%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG2O5ICXWRJCDFEMJKFI2P5OYSI.jpg&h=cbf7df38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FU_WDRnLfbY9fQRQB8t84mj9Iow=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YXTTVRDN25DSHDSGBSWFMZVUQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2